(213, 1, '2019-05-31 14:13:34', '2019-05-31 14:13:34', '<h2>Experience</h2>		\n			<h2>My Work</h2>		\n			<figure><img width=\"1000\" height=\"399\" src=\"portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KdG_H_Closed.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KdG_H_Closed.png 1000w, portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KdG_H_Closed-300x120.png 300w, portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/KdG_H_Closed-768x306.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure><h3>Karel de Grote</h3><p>At Karel de Grote I\'ve completed a lot of projects. Building websites, coding web applications, desinging web pages and even making mobile software. The team at KdG is absolutely amazing.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"190\" src=\"portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/BÃ¦R-logo-300x190.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/BÃ¦R-logo-300x190.png 300w, portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/BÃ¦R-logo-768x487.png 768w, portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/BÃ¦R-logo.png 822w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></figure><h3>BÃR</h3><p>Together with my Scandinavian friends I started a beer brand. In charge of the marketing I made the website and designed all the graphics.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"1892\" height=\"790\" src=\"portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/facebook.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/facebook.png 1892w, portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/facebook-300x125.png 300w, portfoliogoan.1819.goan.hauquier.nxtmediatech.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/facebook-768x321